HOWTO Install a Campsite Demo Site
----------------------------------

Install this demo site after Campsite is successfully installed.

Three step install:
1) Run "[campsite-dir]/bin/campsite-restore -b [backup_file] -e" on the tarball:

   /var/www/campsite/bin/campsite-restore -b NAME_OF_TARBALL.tar.gz -e

   To get help with this command, run it without any arguments.

2) Login to the Campsite Administration (go to http://your_site_name/admin,
   username is "admin", pasword is "admn00").  In the main menu click on
   Content->Publications->Configure.  Change the default site alias to be
   your web site name.

3) Restart apache:
   /etc/init.d/apache restart
   or
   /etc/init.d/httpd restart
